2012-02-18 07:16:48','2012-02-18 07:16:48','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"faq-main\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-header\">Can\'t find the answer to your question below?  \r\n<a href=\"/contact\">Give us a shout</a> and we\'ll be more than happy to answer any questions or concerns you may have. </div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How many people can the photo booth fit?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We can fit you and up to 8 of your guests at one time.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How can I book a photobooth for my event?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Just give us a call or email us with your questions and your reservation inquiries. We can work through the details together and put together the package that best suits your event. We can’t wait to work with you!</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Is a deposit required to reserve a booth?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, we require a $100 deposit to reserve your booth for your event date. Your final payment is required one week before the date of your event.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What methods of payment are available?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Right now we only accept cash, checks and PayPal.  Contact us for more details.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What if I have to cancel or reschedule my event?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will work with you to reschedule your photo booth rental upon availability.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Will there be someone at the event to make sure everything runs smoothly?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will be there to set up the photo booth before your events starts, and will remain on hand throughout your event to make sure everyone is having a great time and that the photobooth stays stocked and running smoothly.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we customize the printout design?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Certainly! We highly suggest that you work with us to customize background and text that is displayed on your prints. Whether you want to use a logo, names and dates, or your favorite quote, we will do everything that we can to make it happen. Virtually anything is possible with the customization level of our prints.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Do we need any special kind of hookup or facilities, to set up the photobooth on-site?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">A normal AC power source is all that is needed, preferably within 10-20 feet.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we get a copy of the images taken by the digital photobooth on a disk?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes all photobooth rentals include a CD or DVD of all the photos taken at high resolution.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-footer\">For any additional questions please call us at 703.898.1702 or <a href=\"/contact\">send us a message!</a> </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-12','','','2012-02-18 07:16:48','2012-02-18 07:16:48','',33,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/33-revision-12/',0,'revision','',0),(271,1,'2012-02-20 16:23:38','2012-02-20 16:23:38','[caption id=\"\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"400\" caption=\"DC Photobooth Owners\"]<img class=\"postimg \" title=\"DC Photobooth Owners\" src=\"http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/all-1-682x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth Owners\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Good morning Brides to be!  You will see these three handsome faces TODAY at the Sheraton Baltimore Bridal Showcase.  Come on in our booth and give it a whirl with our vast array of props!  We look forward to seeing you there!</p>','DC Photobooth LLC Bridal Show','','inherit','open','open','','257-revision-7','','','2012-02-20 16:23:38','2012-02-20 16:23:38','',257,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/257-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2012-0