]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"memberimg3\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"150\" caption=\"Joe Ruzzi\" class=\"memberimg\"]<img src=\"http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/joeruzzi-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Joe Ruzzi - Captain of DC Photobooth\" title=\"Joe Ruzzi\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-111 pageimg memberimg\" />[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','67-revision-36','','','2012-02-23 18:24:38','2012-02-23 18:24:38','',67,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/67-revision-36/',0,'revision','',0),(345,1,'2012-02-23 18:24:54','2012-02-23 18:24:54','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">packages</h1>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section left\">\r\n<h1 class=\"rates-section-header\">basic package</h1>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section-body\">\r\nThe DC Photobooth basic package includes:\r\n<ul class=\"package-details\">\r\n<li>Prompt delivery and set up of booth</li>\r\n<li>1-2 professional booth attendants on-site for duration of the rental</li>\r\n<li>4 hours of unlimited 4-Pose (Black and White or Color) 4” x 6” single prints</li>\r\n<li>3 curtain color options (black, red, creme)</li>\r\n<li>Loads of fun props (we do take requests as well!)</li>\r\n<li>Customizable header/footer design on prints</li>\r\n<li>Customizable electronic slideshow on outer LCD</li>\r\n<li>Following the event, we will host the images in a secure location online (private user name and password will be provided)</li>\r\n<li>1 CD or flash drive with all photos</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section right\">\r\n<h1 class=\"rates-section-header\">available upgrades</h1>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section-body\">\r\nThe following upgrades are also available:\r\n<ul class=\"package-details\">\r\n<li>Double photo prints</li>\r\n<li>Guestbook for guests to leave photos and a note</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<img src=\"http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/guestbook-2-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth Guest Book\" title=\"DC Photobooth Guest Book\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-148 pageimg\" />\r\n</div>','Packages','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-10','','','2012-02-23 18:24:54','2012-02-23 18:24:54','',28,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/28-revision-10/',0,'revision','',0),(346,1,'2012-02-20 20:25:14','2012-02-20 20:25:14','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"faq-main\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-header\">Can\'t find the answer to your question below?  \r\n<a href=\"/contact\">Give us a shout</a> and we\'ll be more than happy to answer any questions or concerns you may have. </div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How many people can the photo booth fit?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We can fit you and up to 8 of your guests at one time.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How can I book a photobooth for my event?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Just give us a call or email us with your questions and your reservation inquiries. We can work through the details together and put together the package that best suits your event. We can’t wait to work with you!</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Is a deposit required to reserve a booth?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, we require a $100 deposit with the signed contract to reserve your booth for your event date. Your final payment is required two weeks before the date of your event.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What methods of payment are available?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Right now we only accept cash, checks and PayPal.  Contact us for more details.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What if I have to cancel or reschedule my event?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will work with you to reschedule your photo booth rental upon availability.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Will there be someone at the event to make sure everything runs smoothly?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will be there to set up the photo booth before your events starts, and will remain on hand throughout your event to make sure everyone is having a great time and that the photobooth stays stocked and running smoothly.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we customize the printout design?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Certainly! We highly suggest that you work with us to customize background and text that is displayed on your prints. Whether you want to use a logo, names and dates, or your favorite quote, we will do everything that we can to make it happen. Virtually anything is possible with the customization level of our prints.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Do we need any special kind of hookup or facilities, to set up the photobooth on-site?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">A normal AC power source is all that is needed, preferably within 10-20 feet.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we get a copy of the images taken by the digital photobooth on a disk?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes all photobooth rentals include a CD or DVD of all the photos taken at high resolution.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-footer\">For any additional questions please call us at 703.898.1702 or <a href=\"/contact\">send us a message!</a> </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-13','','','2012-02-20 20:25:14','2012-02-20 20:25:14','',33,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/33-revision-13/',0,'revision','',0),(347,1,'2012-02-22 00:32:19','2012-02-22 00:32:19','[caption id=\"attachment_48\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\" caption=\"Introducing the first booth for DC Photobooth\"]<img class=\"wp-image-48 postimg    \" title=\"DC Photobooth Large\" src=\"http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Booth-Mock-up1-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"First Booth for DC Photobooth\" width=\"300\" height=\"450\" />[/caption]\r\n\r\nIntroducing the first booth for DC Photobooth! This booth features a state of the art camera and can fit up to 20 people at once! The booth decor is fully customizable for your event. Choose your curtain color and featured image for the front of the both. Servicing the Washington D.C., Virginia and Maryland areas, this booth is sure to be the hit of your next event!','DC Photobooth\'s First Booth!','','inherit','open','open','','47-revision-15','','','2012-02-22 00:32:19','2012-02-22 00:32:19','',47,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/blog/47-revision-15/',0,'revision','',0),(351,1,'2012-02-23 22:19:00','2012-02-23 22:19:00','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">packages</h1><div style=\"clear:both\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section left\">\r\n<h1 class=\"rates-section-header\">basic package</h1>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section-body\">\r\nThe DC Photobooth basic package includes:\r\n<ul class=\"package-details\">\r\n<li>Prompt delivery and set up of booth</li>\r\n<li>1-2 professional booth attendants on-site for duration of the rental</li>\r\n<li>4 hours of unlimited 4-Pose (Black and White or Color) 4” x 6” single prints</li>\r\n<li>3 curtain color options (black, red, creme)</li>\r\n<li>Loads of fun props (we do take requests as well!)</li>\r\n<li>Customizable header/footer design on prints</li>\r\n<li>Customizable electronic slideshow on outer LCD</li>\r\n<li>Following the event, we will host the images in a secure location online (private user name and password will be provided)</li>\r\n<li>1 CD or flash drive with all photos</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section right\">\r\n<h1 class=\"rates-section-header\">available upgrades</h1>\r\n<div class=\"rates-section-body\">\r\nThe following upgrades are also available:\r\n<ul class=\"package-details\">\r\n<li>Double photo prints</li>\r\n<li>Guestbook for guests to leave photos and a note</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<img src=\"http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/guestbook-2-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth Guest Book\" title=\